{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him I was studying engineering.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they kidded me about many things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they didn't abuse us in any other way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all youngsters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't have been more than 17, 18, in these new fancy uniforms, having the order to get us to some point where they transferred us onto the-- into the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was there that I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I helped many of the older people get up onto this cattle car.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Remember, from the street-- from the ground onto this door of the cattle car is quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these old people couldn't negotiate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would hit them with the rifle butt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Speed up, speed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would stand-- be standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was the only one, I must admit, who grabbed them by the seat and helped them up to climb in there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't-- they somehow let me do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I look back, it was a stupid thing to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the same--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were all in the black SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you the nationality.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could have been Czech, for what I know, or Pollacks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows who volunteered once this great thing happened, don't you see?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The mass hysteria.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in-- on the car, it says, 6 horses or 48 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I assure you, it was more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a trip that seemed to take forever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The stench was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were fainting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was young and strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a healthy young man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we finally-- we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rumors-- they're sending us to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
